	   <tr><td colspan=2>- Spirit of Wolf :<br>Classes: Rng(L30) Dru(L14) Shm(L9) Bst(L30)<br>Increase Movement between 34% (L9) to 55% (L50)<br>Spell Duration: 360 ticks (36 minutes)<br>Casting Time: 4.50 seconds<br>Note: Shamans in one of their EPIC Step , receive some Boots with a Self Instant SoW Effect <br><br><br>- Scale of Wolf (aka The SoW for Travel):<br>Classes: Dru(L29) Shm(L24)<br>Increase Movement between 57% (L24) to 70% (L50)<br>Negate if you start to Combat or Cast (Note: dont negate if you are attacked, only if you attack)<br>Spell Duration: 450 ticks (45 minutes)<br>Casting Time: 4.50 seconds<br>FOR THIS EARRING Casting Time: (i have it) it seems to be the same of the spell<br><br>- Spirit of Cheetah (aka The SoW for Escape):<br><br>Classes: Dru(L24) Shm(L24)<br>Increase Movement between 99% (L24) to 115% (L40)<br>Spell Duration: 8 ticks (48 seconds)<br>Casting Time: 0.50 seconds<br>Recast Delay: 10 minutes<br><br><br>- Journeyman and Traveler Boots&nbsp;&nbsp;Effect<br>Increase Movement by 35% (L1)<br>Spell Duration: 180 ticks (18.0 minutes)<br><br><br>Note: ALL this effects have a Casting Area Restriction: Outdoor<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
